Dependencies:
g++
libnoise (libraries and headers)
python2.7
python2.7-tk
python-imaging-tk
cmake

To install dependencies on Ubuntu 11.04:
sudo apt-get install libnoise-dev python2.7-tk python-imaging-tk -y

To checkout from git:
git clone git://github.com/sbobovyc/DCS.git

To compile(Linux):
cd DCS/DCS/utils
mkdir build
cd build
cmake ..
make

To compile(Windows)
cd DCS\DCS\utils
mkdir build
cd build
cmake -G "MinGW Makefiles" -DNOISE_INCLUDE_DIR=/c/libnoise -DNOISE_LIBRARY=/c/libnoise/src ..
make


To run gui:
bash run-DCS-app.sh

